## The "Repeat Until It's Your Thing" Rule

**Don't tell each story once. Tell it 10 times in different forms.**

| Form | Example |
|------|---------|
| Text post | Full narrative |
| Carousel | Steps/journey version |
| Quote graphic | Key line from story |
| Video | Spoken version |
| Reply | Reference in comments |
| Podcast | Extended version |

